            "id": 6415272,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 崇越(5434)股價拉至漲停，漲停價402.0元，成交2,390張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>崇越(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5434:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5434\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5434-TW</a>)10日13:14上漲36.5元，股價漲停報402.0元，委買2張、委賣1張，成交2,390張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為半導體與光電相關產品。電子材料。環境工程。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>崇越(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5434:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5434\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5434-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲10.26%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲7.03%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+1,746 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+1,470 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+132 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+144 張</li> <li>融資增減：+133 張</li> <li>融券增減：+5 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
